altername_name: フラッシュセガサターン おちかづき編
name: Flash Sega Saturn: Ochikadzuki-hen
overview: Flash Sega Saturn: Ochikadzuki-hen (フラッシュセガサターン おちかづき編) is a Japanese Sega Saturn demo disc. Unlike other Flash Sega Saturn series, this disc was bundled with the Saturn hardware. Playable Demos included: Saturn Bomberman Videos included: Cyber Troopers Virtual-On Sakura Taisen Tengai Makyou: Daiyon no Mokushiroku
